Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:23.55,names,,0,0,0,,马尔·亚迪特星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:19.30,names,,0,0,0,,齐格贝尔特·塞德利兹准将
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:06.49,names,,0,0,0,,22:50
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:21.85,names,,0,0,0,,荷夫麦斯塔中将
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:46.17,names,,0,0,0,,23:10
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:30.20,names,,0,0,0,,艾玛森中校
